{"tid":737008,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲性學專家：「淨同伴侶扑嘢係違反自然，傻嘅先會結婚」","createTime":"2018-07-10T16:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T04:21:37.000Z","uid":1886,"like":49,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d147599f29e108e06526952de0a107a9053fbc1b","tid":737008,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:00:39.000Z","msg":"澳洲一名性學專家娜迪雅（Nadia Bokody）近日PO文說出了一段驚人的言論，她表示其實婚姻制度根本不符合我們現在的價值觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，還強調人類根本不適合走入婚姻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為「一直和同一個人進行性行為是有違自然的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一夫一妻制根本不存在於我們的DNA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180710/640_6ada94e87477c0536111744bc27eccab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180710%2F640_6ada94e87477c0536111744bc27eccab.jpg&h=f02b2e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">澳洲性學專家娜迪亞近日發文直言，自願選擇結婚、受過教育的成年人都是傻蛋。</span></div><br />\n<br />\nNadia Bokody 認為婚姻制度根本不不符合現代的價值觀，尤其是傳統的婚禮誓言，因為其中包含「擁有」，這代表另一個人將「持有」自己的所有權，她直言這個想法是「古老的廢話」，因為現代人的壽命比起過去長許多，這意味著人類必須和伴侶共度更多時間，所做的犧牲比以往更多，她直言「這只是受虐狂」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=401898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D401898&d=6W8%2BLKhIc92RDcCqXmxrmfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=c5a04f40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D401898&h=74e1b2a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=401898</a>"},{"pid":"4ee730ea9919bcc31f918609e5ae394c1cdcff14","tid":737008,"uid":3962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"快點無違我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4bd82b905ae65b6574fc73c35c255475fdab26","tid":737008,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:01:58.000Z","msg":"快點研究我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90dbfc1d520fdf27ae1a8454acb21006d8aa3833","tid":737008,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:02:36.000Z","msg":"根據《每日郵報》報導，澳洲性學專家娜迪亞近日公開PO文，直言受過教育又自願走入婚姻的成年人都是傻蛋，「其實我們很多人都這樣想過，只是擔心會被其他人指指點點，所以很少說出來！」根據研究顯示，1/3的婚姻關係都曾收到伴侶出軌影響，1/5的人此時此時就在出軌中，娜迪亞強調她研究人類關係多年，最後的結論就是人類並非生來就應與同一個人過一生的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/07/10/1437871-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2F1437871-XXL.jpg&h=eead6a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲娜迪雅表示人類基因裡沒有一夫一妻制。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n「我媽媽就曾說過，和一個讓你非常痛苦的人在一起是沒有意義的。」娜迪亞指出，現代人壽命越來越長，當年婚姻制度出現時，夫妻不喜歡彼此頂多只要忍10年、20年，但現在一忍就要忍3、40年，因此才會衍生價值十幾億美元的情趣用品市場，「考慮到以上這些因素之後，出現開放婚姻及單身主義等新的關係模式也就不奇怪了。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180710/1388311/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180710%2F1388311%2F&d=6W8%2BLKhIc92RDcCqXmxrmfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=9eb2b551\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180710%2F1388311%2F&h=c649afb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180710/1388311/</a>"},{"pid":"ee488a51ae8c8cf9798e69a8dcbb0fd13c6b71c8","tid":737008,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c4bd82b905ae65b6574fc73c35c255475fdab26","tid":737008,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:01:58.000Z","msg":"快點研究我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:03:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/07/10/1437870-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2F1437870-XXL.jpg&h=750826e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">不過娜迪雅也說，自己並非是不欣賞真愛，也不會不接受那些進入婚姻且遵守一夫一妻制的人，只是現在時代已經改變了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，她認為找一個人陪她度過餘生，只是一種幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</span></div>"},{"pid":"70fcd6b65472d366773d80f81e9d8fb54e99133c","tid":737008,"uid":178332,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:04:35.000Z","msg":"第一張相同第二第三張差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a8a545a2b5d9a1cef45f8a469a199310f578f2","tid":737008,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:09:01.000Z","msg":"婚姻制度係用黎保障弱者,, 等弱者都有機會有伴侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3127046e5c7f4308b7480adaf862ebfae23412a","tid":737008,"uid":123264,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:10:49.000Z","msg":"人類基因無禁止強姦咁係咪可以周圍強姦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37afcdcdb821d1d4bff70deceff36850d1cdf55","tid":737008,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219aff9a2a195f8342f6602bee171a1124d4ef90","tid":737008,"uid":58316,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:13:16.000Z","msg":"冇抵觸<br />\n結婚都可以換妻可以多p<br />\n有d男人默許老婆出去